<br>
Both Blunt and Pierce have reactionary styles that include a stun. Pierce's is off of an Evade which since Firbolg's have less Dexterity and Quickness than other races will Evade less. While Blunt's is based off of Parry which is based off your Dexterity and Pary spec.<br>
<br>
